Telkom has launched its Big Deal for August 2019. This deal allows users to sign up for 20GB Anytime and 20GB Night Surfer LTE data for R249 per month on a 24-month contract. The following is included in the August 2019 Big Deal: The Netflix voucher covers August to October and is available to both new and existing Netflix subscribers. Telkom recommends that users check that their area is covered before signing up to this product. This Big Deal is subject to Telkom’s Acceptable Usage Policy and is available until 31 August 2019. 